'''Spomenka Štimec''' (born 4 January 1949) is a Croatian writer, one of the most acclaimed contemporary writers in [[Esperanto]],<ref>{{cite encyclopedia|title=Štimec, Spomenka|encyclopedia=Concise Encyclopedia of the Original Literature of Esperanto, 1887-2007|last=Sutton|first=Geoffrey|publisher=Mondial|location=New York|year=2008}}</ref> and also significant to Esperanto in Croatia.<ref>[http://www.huffingtonpost.com/huff-wires/20091215/eu-poland-esperanto/ The Huffington Post]</ref> She shared a [[:d:Q12344841|FAME Award]].

